  "description": "A wide shot of a rocky beach with two children standing near the water's edge. The beach is composed of dark, grainy sand. The ocean is a mix of turquoise and deep blue, with white foam where the waves break. Several large, dark rock formations rise out of the water, creating a dramatic backdrop. The children, one wearing a blue jacket and the other a red jacket, are facing the water, appearing to observe something. The sky is clear and blue. The overall scene conveys a sense of spaciousness and natural beauty.",
